msgid "CF Rules Wizard"
msgstr "CF Regler Guide"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:41
msgid "You do not have sufficient permissions to access this page."
msgstr "Du har ikke tilstrækkelige rettigheder til at få adgang til denne side."

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:46
msgid "Created by Rob Marlbrough at"
msgstr "Oprettet af Rob Marlbrough hos"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:46
