msgstr "Press Wizards - WordPress Design, Hosting og Vedligeholdelse"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:50 cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:104
msgid ""
"If this plugin saves you time, helps your clients, or helps you do better "
"work, I'd appreciate it."
msgstr ""
"Hvis dette plugin sparer dig tid, hjælper dine kunder, eller hjælper dig med "
"at gøre et bedre stykke arbejde, ville jeg sætte pris på det."

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:62
msgid "Select Domains to Reset WAF Custom Rules on:"
msgstr "Vælg domæner for at nulstille WAF tilpassede regler på:"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:65
msgid "Select All"
msgstr "Vælg Alle"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:76
msgid "Create/Overwrite All WAF Rules"
msgstr "Opret/Overskriv Alle WAF Regler"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:92
msgid "Save Settings"
msgstr "Gem Indstillinger"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:99
msgid "Delete Settings"
msgstr "Slet Indstillinger"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:108
msgid "Based on"
msgstr "Baseret på"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:108
msgid "Troy Glancy's superb Cloudflare WAF Rules v3"
msgstr "Troy Glancys fremragende Cloudflare WAF Regler v3"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:139
msgid "Cloudflare WAF Rules Wizard settings have been deleted."
msgstr "Cloudflare WAF Regler Guide indstillinger er blevet slettet."

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:145
msgid "Enter your Cloudflare API Key and Email address, and the Account ID."
msgstr "Indtast din Cloudflare API-nøgle og e-mailadresse samt konto-ID."

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:146
msgid ""
"When you Save the settings, it will get all the domains under the account ID, "
"and you can select the ones you want CF WAF custom rules created in."
msgstr ""
"Når du gemmer indstillingerne, vil den hente alle domæner under konto-ID'et, "
"og du kan vælge dem, du ønsker CF WAF tilpassede regler oprettet i."

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:147
msgid "Dig into Troy's WAF Rules v3 - each rule explained in detail"
msgstr "Dyk ned i Troys WAF Regler v3 - hver regel forklaret i detaljer"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:147
msgid ""
"You can further customize the rules after they are created directly in "
"Cloudflare under Security > WAF > Custom rules."
msgstr ""
"Du kan yderligere tilpasse reglerne, efter de er oprettet direkte i "
"Cloudflare under Sikkerhed > WAF > Tilpassede regler."

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:148
msgid ""
"NOTE: It resets all WAF custom rules! If any other WAF Custom Rules exist for "
"that domain, it will erase them, and create 5 new rules. IMPORTANT: Use at "
"your own risk!"
msgstr ""
"BEMÆRK: Det nulstiller alle WAF tilpassede regler! Hvis der findes andre WAF "
"Tilpassede Regler for det domæne, vil de blive slettet, og 5 nye regler vil "
"blive oprettet. VIGTIGT: Brug på eget ansvar!"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:149
msgid ""
"Security Tip: Click the Delete Settings button after you are done using this "
"plugin to remove your credentials. They are not encrypted when stored. Maybe "
"future versions will encrypt, delete the options on deactivation, etc. Right "
"now it is a quick and simple plugin for you to use and then remove."
msgstr ""
"Sikkerhedstip: Klik på knappen Slet Indstillinger, når du er færdig med at "
"bruge dette plugin for at fjerne dine legitimationsoplysninger. De er ikke "
"krypteret, når de gemmes. Måske vil fremtidige versioner kryptere, slette "
"mulighederne ved deaktivering osv. Lige nu er det et hurtigt og enkelt plugin "
"for dig at bruge og derefter fjerne."

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:230
msgid "Built-in User Agents:"
msgstr "Indbyggede Brugeragenter:"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:236
msgid "Custom User Agents:"
msgstr "Tilpassede Brugeragenter:"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:237
msgid ""
"Enter one User Agent per line. Only alphanumeric characters, spaces, "
"underscores, and hyphens are allowed."
msgstr ""
"Indtast én Brugeragent pr. linje. Kun alfanumeriske tegn, mellemrum, "
"understregninger og bindestreger er tilladt."

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:238
msgid "Enter one User Agent per line"
msgstr "Indtast én Brugeragent pr. linje"

#: cloudflare_waf_rules_wizard.php:317
msgid "Please enter all the required fields."
msgstr "Indtast venligst alle de nødvendige felter."

